{"id":272862,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/【网络民议】南周新年献辞事件网民回应集锦（二/","date":"2013-01-07T03:00:17Z","modified":"2014-10-17T20:44:35Z","title":"【网络民议】南周新年献辞事件网民回应集锦图集（二）","content":"<p>“你们知道，如果没有每一年的新年献词，那些将身心托付于新闻的中国人，无法去诉说自己的情怀，无法去寻找自身的希望，无法去在漫漫人海中寻求虚无缥缈的归属感…… 也许，你们不知道《南方周末》，但是你应该知道他所追求的一切，自由，民主，幸福以及理想。也许，你们不知道《南方周末》，但是你应该知道他的对手。”</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/img-0beebcd55c2986c5b86f61f76a6e4010.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-272868\" title=\"img-0beebcd55c2986c5b86f61f76a6e4010\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/img-0beebcd55c2986c5b86f61f76a6e4010.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"442\" height=\"305\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/img-0beebcd55c2986c5b86f61f76a6e4010.jpg 442w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/img-0beebcd55c2986c5b86f61f76a6e4010-300x207.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 442px) 100vw, 442px\" /></a></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_273139\" style=\"width: 591px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/编辑部.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-273139\" title=\"编辑部\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/编辑部.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"581\" height=\"436\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/编辑部.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/编辑部-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 581px) 100vw, 581px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">南周编辑部对背黑锅事件的抗议</p></div>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/img-e8c50cafaca5c6504ac1827cbcd5eed3.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-272869\" title=\"img-e8c50cafaca5c6504ac1827cbcd5eed3\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/img-e8c50cafaca5c6504ac1827cbcd5eed3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"460\" height=\"423\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/img-e8c50cafaca5c6504ac1827cbcd5eed3.jpg 460w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/img-e8c50cafaca5c6504ac1827cbcd5eed3-300x275.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 460px) 100vw, 460px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/img-730e9efa76047088fb5602722e901f6f-1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-272871\" title=\"img-730e9efa76047088fb5602722e901f6f (1)\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/img-730e9efa76047088fb5602722e901f6f-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"515\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/img-730e9efa76047088fb5602722e901f6f-1.jpg 515w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/img-730e9efa76047088fb5602722e901f6f-1-280x300.jpg 280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 515px) 100vw, 515px\" /></a></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_273131\" style=\"width: 594px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/百度百科.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-273131\" title=\"百度百科\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/百度百科.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"584\" height=\"463\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/百度百科.jpg 584w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/百度百科-300x237.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 584px) 100vw, 584px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">截图所含的百度百科词条内容已在该页面上消失。百度百科上经常会出现一些网民自发更新的时事内容，但一般都会在经过广泛传播后被删除。</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_273138\" style=\"width: 608px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/李铁1.jpg\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-273138\" title=\"李铁\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/李铁1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"598\" height=\"376\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/李铁1.jpg 598w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/李铁1-300x188.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 598px) 100vw, 598px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">南周编辑部被迫背黑锅事件后，不少南周编辑记者都提出罢工以示抗议。评论员李铁就是其中一位。</p></div>\n<p><a hre